About Aralez
The combination of POZEN and Tribute Pharmaceuticals represents an important strategic transformation that created Aralez Pharmaceuticals, a specialty pharmaceutical company with a compelling growth platform.






Our Portfolio
The Aralez portfolio of approved and investigational products is anchored in cardiovascular disease therapies, with a significant pain treatment franchise, and plans for continued development and growth in these and other specialty areas.






For Investors
Aralez is focused on delivering meaningful products to improve patients’ lives while growing shareholder value in short, medium and long-term. Investor information such as press releases, presentations and webcasts can be found in this section.



























