aralez pharmaceuticals inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Health Care
Industry: Biotech & Pharma
Sub-Industry: Specialty Pharma
Aralez Pharmaceuticals Inc. operates as a pharmaceutical company. The Company focuses on acquiring, developing, and commercializing products primarily in cardiovascular, pain, and other specialty areas. Aralez Pharmaceuticals serves customers worldwide.




