			Company Description 
		


                Aralez Pharmaceuticals Inc. operates as a pharmaceutical company. It focuses on the development, acquisition, and commercialization of cardiovascular, pain, and other product therapies. The company is founded on December 2, 2015 and is headquartered in Ontario, Canada.^ ^ ^ ^ ^ ^ ^
            




